column5: My secondary prize from WFN arrived yesterday by FedEx! I received a $250.00 gift card for Bass Pro Shops.  Just wanted to thank all the good folks on here and a few in particular that went way and beyond to help me stay in the top ten (actually 3rd) right up until the end.  Thanks again everyone!
Congrates!  Sounds like a $500 trip to BPS!!!!  I voted when I could.
Gee .... that isn't gonna go too far when everyone that voted greets you at the door to BPS.....
Congratulations Brian, I'm happy for you.
Great job OFC! See we can make differences here. One happy angler later OFC had the power to make it happen!
